2D Plotter  – (Ongoing)

• Developing a 2D plotter system by converting input images into G-code using Inkscape and GRBL workflow
• Implementing motion control by interfacing Arduino with servo motors for precise path execution
• Understanding and analysing G-code instructions for coordinated multi-axis movement
• Currently working on hardware integration and control logic for accurate plotting
• Planned assembly and testing of complete system for real-time drawing applications
